❌ Common Beginner Mistakes

-❌ Python not installed

-❌ Python not added to PATH

-❌ Python interpreter not selected

-❌ Running code outside the project folder

If something doesn’t work, check these first.

✅ What You Should Know Before Moving On

Before continuing:

✔️ VS Code is installed

✔️ Python extension is installed

✔️ Python interpreter is selected

✔️ You can run a .py file

